name: PreOrder Mystery Packs - Tiffany Atkin
description:
To celebrate the 'charlie heartbreaker featuring...' range, a very limited number of 'Mystery Packs' have been made available. 

These packs are a pre-order & will contain a random mix of goodies from you chosen artist! They will be forwarded to you as soon as they are available, fresh before anyone else can get their hands on them! 

Select from 'Bows Only' or a 'Random Mix'! 
Whatever you choose, you will not be disappointed. 

What you get:
Bows Only (RRP $50.00)
5 random bows featuring designs from Tiffany Atkin

Random Mix (RRP min $50.00)
5 random pieces featuring designs from Tiffany Atkin (*can include bows, earrings, & brooches)

Get more information on Tiffany Atkin here: https://www.facebook.com/tiffany.atkin.design
